intent.user_query: What is the average unit price of each product sold?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, AVG(sd.UnitPrice) AS AverageUnitPrice FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, AVG(sd.UnitPrice) AS AverageUnitPrice FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
